Components of Selenium:
  Selenium IDE {Selenium 1}
  Selenium RC  {Selenium 2}
  Selenium WebDriver  {Selenium 3} --> {Selenium 4.x}
  Selenium Grid

Selenium is an Open Source Tool
  Visualize the Source code
  Customize the code
  Contribute to the code

It's also a free License Tool:
Selenium is a free tool

Supports multiple browsers: Chrome/Firefox/Safari/Edge/IE/Opera
Supports Operating System or OS: Windows/Mac/Linux [Unix]
Supports Programming Languages: Java,C#, Python, Ruby, Php, JS

W3C protocol: World Wide Web Consortium
===================================================================================================
Disadvantages of Selenium
1.  To automate only Web Applications
2.  We cannot automate APIs using Selenium

